      <title>新西兰航空上半年利润下降38%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-first-half-profit-drops-38-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，新西兰航空报告称，受通胀压力和持续的供应链问题（主要是普惠公司）的影响，其半年度利润下降了 38%。惠特尼公司 A321neo 机队的发动机维护要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-first-half-profit-drops-38-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 19:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰逮捕了参与 Lockbit 网络犯罪行动的父子二人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/ukraine-arrests-father-son-duo-lockbit-cybercrime-bust-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰警方周三表示，他们逮捕了网络犯罪团伙 Lockbit 的一对父子，本周早些时候，英国国家犯罪局和联邦调查局领导的国际执法行动扰乱了该团伙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/ukraine-arrests-father-son-duo-lockbit-cybercrime-bust-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔成为微软代工客户，有望超越台积电</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-expects-overtake-tsmc-making-fastest-chips-this-year-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔周三表示，微软计划利用其服务制造定制计算芯片，该公司预计在 2025 年内部最后期限之前，在先进芯片制造领域超越其最大竞争对手台积电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-expects-overtake-tsmc-making-fastest-chips-this-year-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:50:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>各方达成协议后巴基斯坦经历了“过山车”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-roller-coaster-ride-after-parties-strike-deal-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦人民党一位高级官员周三表示，巴基斯坦两个政党之间组建联合政府的协议将基于其中一个政党巴基斯坦人民党的有条件支持，该党将根据具体情况审查决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-roller-coaster-ride-after-parties-strike-deal-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高管表示，劳斯莱斯喷气发动机价格上涨不会阻碍高需求下的销售</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rolls-royce-jet-engine-price-hikes-not-impeding-sales-amid-high-demand-exec-says-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，劳斯莱斯一位高级管理人员对路透社表示，由于全行业对新飞机和发动机的需求巨大，劳斯莱斯飞机发动机的价格上涨并没有阻碍销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rolls-royce-jet-engine-price-hikes-not-impeding-sales-amid-high-demand-exec-says-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Piedmont Lithium 将以 3900 万美元出售 Sayona Mining 剩余股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/piedmont-lithium-sell-remaining-stake-sayona-mining-39-mln-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国矿商 Piedmont Lithium 周三表示，将以约 5,990 万澳元（合 3,928 万美元）的价格出售其在澳大利亚矿商 Sayona Mining 的剩余股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/piedmont-lithium-sell-remaining-stake-sayona-mining-39-mln-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 13:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公司文件显示，三星电子在第四季度出售了剩余的 ASML 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/samsung-electronics-sold-remaining-asml-shares-q4-company-filing-shows-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国三星电子周三提交的一份公司文件显示，去年第四季度，该公司出售了其在半导体制造设备制造商 ASML 的全部剩余股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/samsung-electronics-sold-remaining-asml-shares-q4-company-filing-shows-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚普拉博沃学校供餐计划第一年耗资 77 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-prabowos-school-meal-programme-cost-77-bln-first-year-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚新任总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 的团队周三表示，其计划第一年将耗资高达 120 万亿卢比（76.8 亿美元），为学校提供免费午餐和牛奶。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-prabowos-school-meal-programme-cost-77-bln-first-year-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:47:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国律师称阿桑奇因“不加区别地”公布消息来源姓名而被通缉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/assange-charged-indiscriminately-publishing-sources-names-us-lawyers-say-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表美国的律师周三表示，朱利安·阿桑奇因公布消息来源的姓名而不是他的政治观点而受到起诉，这位维基解密创始人阻止他从英国引渡的最新斗争已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/assange-charged-indiscriminately-publishing-sources-names-us-lawyers-say-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:14:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港科学家为濒临灭绝的鲎寻求好运</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/hong-kong-scientists-seek-good-fortune-endangered-horseshoe-crabs-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港自然资源保护主义者周三开始在水下追踪濒临灭绝的鲎（这种鲎的历史可以追溯到恐龙出现之前），以帮助它们在现代生活的危险中生存下来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/hong-kong-scientists-seek-good-fortune-endangered-horseshoe-crabs-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
